# ============================================================================
# Custom AI Instructions (User-Specific)
# ============================================================================
# The .ai-iap-custom/ directory allows you to extend or override core files
# without modifying the plugin's lib/ (ensures safe updates)
#
# Options:
# - Option A (Default): Keep custom files local (git ignored)
# - Option B: Share with team (remove .ai-iap-custom/ from gitignore)
# ============================================================================

# Ignore custom files (keep local only)
.ai-iap-custom/**

# BUT: Always include example files for reference
!.ai-iap-custom/
!.ai-iap-custom/rules/
!.ai-iap-custom/rules/**/
!.ai-iap-custom/processes/
!.ai-iap-custom/processes/**/
!.ai-iap-custom/functions/
!.ai-iap-custom/functions/**/
!.ai-iap-custom/*.example.*
!.ai-iap-custom/**/*.example.*
!.ai-iap-custom/README.md
!.ai-iap-custom/INDEX.md
!.ai-iap-custom/functions/INDEX.md
